00:23:14,934 --> 00:23:18,872
{\an1}NARUTO: Next time on Naruto:
Shippuden, Kakashi Hatake,

426
00:23:18,906 --> 00:23:20,406
{\an1}the Jounin in Charge.

427
00:23:20,439 --> 00:23:23,343
{\an1}-This looks like it's
going to be troublesome.

